title: Construction Site with Excavators
description: The image shows a construction site with two yellow excavators. One excavator is actively working on a dirt mound, while the other is positioned nearby. In the foreground, there is a water body with a stone embankment, and in the background, a clear blue sky is visible.

title: Dredging Boat on Water
description: A dredging boat is anchored in a body of water, with a clear blue sky and a few clouds in the background. The boat has a large arm extending over the water, likely for dredging purposes, and is equipped with various machinery and tanks. In the distance, other boats can be seen on the water.

title: Flood Warning Sign
description: A triangular warning sign with a red border. The sign features a black silhouette of a house partially submerged in blue water, indicating a flood hazard.

title: Parliament Chamber
description: An interior view of a parliamentary chamber featuring rows of wooden seating arranged in a semi-circular layout. The chamber includes a central podium with a table and chairs, and the walls are adorned with a subtle design. The seating is primarily blue, and the overall atmosphere is formal and organized.
